---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Coastal Limestone — Peel region's trusted earthworks and limestone retaining wall specialists.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Peel region's trusted name in earthworks and limestone retaining walls</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Coastal Limestone has been operating in and in and around the Peel for over 15 years. What started as a one-man bobcat operation has grown into a full-service earthworks and landscaping business — without losing the personal touch that got us here.</p>
        <p>We take on everything from small residential retaining wall jobs to large-scale commercial site preparation. The same care, the same quality, every time.</p>
        <p>We believe in doing the job properly — which means proper drainage behind every wall, proper compaction on every pad, and leaving every site clean when we finish. That approach has earned us repeat customers and referrals right across the Peel region.</p>

        <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
        <div class="values">
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Quality Materials</h3>
            <p>We use only quality Peel limestone and locally sourced materials. No shortcuts on what goes into your job.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Honest Pricing</h3>
            <p>We quote the real price — not a lowball estimate that grows when the invoice arrives. What we quote is what you pay.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Clean Sites</h3>
            <p>We leave every site clean, clear and safe. Rubble removed, access maintained, ready for the next trade.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Done Once, Done Right</h3>
            <p>We build it to last. No call-backs, no fixing problems we should have solved the first time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">15+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years in Business</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">500+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Retaining Walls Built</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-num">100%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Customer Satisfaction</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.page-header { background: var(--dark); color: white; padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem; text-align: center; }
.page-header h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: white; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.page-header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

.about-content { padding: 4rem 0; }
.container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
.about-text h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--stone); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; }
.about-text h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.about-text p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }

.values { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.value { background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 3px solid var(--rust); }
.value h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--stone); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.value p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-light); margin: 0; }

.stats { background: var(--stone); padding: 4rem 2rem; }
.stats-grid { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.stat { text-align: center; }
.stat-num { display: block; font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--limestone); }
.stat-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .values { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .stats-grid { gap: 2rem; }
}
</style>